            <title><![CDATA[无惊无险又到5点半！摸鱼洗杯子等下班啦[开学季] 上班前洗杯子、下班后洗杯子，哪个更卫生？搬砖人专用小科普来一波[打工人]使用完的杯子一定要当天清洗。研究发...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[无惊无险又到5点半！摸鱼洗杯子等下班啦<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[开学季]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/72/2021_kaixueji_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> 上班前洗杯子、下班后洗杯子，哪个更卫生？搬砖人专用小科普来一波<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[打工人]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/a1/2023_earner_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>使用完的杯子一定要当天清洗。研究发现，24小时内，水的细菌数量会从600个增加至1100个，大麦茶会从600个增加至3700个，可乐、纯橙汁和牛奶咖啡的细菌分别会从600个增加到249.38万、250.39万和517.59万个……<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[衰]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shuai-285d2d97c7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>杯里长时间处于潮湿状态，很容易培养霉菌和细菌，尤其是挤压型、螺旋型等瓶口的杯子，更容易藏污纳垢，使革兰氏阴性菌更难清除。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[并不简单]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bingbujiandan-9955880b30.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（广东疾控）<img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hkd9gq7s85j20m80dedhi.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
