            <title><![CDATA[#反复烧水会增加致癌物质吗#[费解]👇🏻抛开计量谈毒性都是耍流氓！研究显示，烧开1次的水，与烧开20次的水，亚硝酸盐含量分别为 0.021mg/L 与 0.038mg/L，远...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8F%8D%E5%A4%8D%E7%83%A7%E6%B0%B4%E4%BC%9A%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E8%87%B4%E7%99%8C%E7%89%A9%E8%B4%A8%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8F%8D%E5%A4%8D%E7%83%A7%E6%B0%B4%E4%BC%9A%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E8%87%B4%E7%99%8C%E7%89%A9%E8%B4%A8%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#反复烧水会增加致癌物质吗#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[费解]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_feijie-c1df37ef03.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>👇🏻<br><br>抛开计量谈毒性都是耍流氓！研究显示，烧开1次的水，与烧开20次的水，亚硝酸盐含量分别为 0.021mg/L 与 0.038mg/L，远远低于国家生活用水的标准1mg/L。因此，水烧开多次，本身是不会影响到健康情况的。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（科学辟谣） <img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hkcwy9fdh1j20hs0f5abb.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
